{# ── Three Benefit Cards ── #}
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header text-center" style="max-width:640px;margin:0 auto var(--space-xl);">
      <h2>What in-district access means for Pflugerville</h2>
      <p>ACC is not just college. It trains electricians, nurses, welders, HVAC technicians, cybersecurity specialists, and advanced manufacturing workers. In-district status means Pflugerville residents get equal access at equal rates.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card-grid">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">$</div>
        <h3>Close the cost gap</h3>
        <p>In-district tuition is $85/credit hour. Pflugerville residents currently pay $286. That $201 per credit hour difference costs a full-time student $6,030 per year, and over $12,000 for a two-year associate degree.</p>
        <a href="/calculator/" class="card-link">Calculate your savings &rarr;</a>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">&#9881;</div>
        <h3>Workforce and trades</h3>
        <p>ACC offers 100+ programs: welding, HVAC, plumbing, nursing through BSN, cybersecurity, advanced manufacturing, culinary arts. PfISD already runs Career Academies with ACC. In-district makes the pipeline affordable.</p>
        <a href="/workforce-and-trades/" class="card-link">See programs &rarr;</a>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">&#10003;</div>
        <h3>Proof it works</h3>
        <p>Lockhart joined the ACC district in November 2024. Enrollment tripled in one year. ACC opened a new campus. Elgin joined in 2010 and saw a 58% enrollment jump with a full campus by 2013. Every community that voted yes got results.</p>
        <a href="/why-this-matters/" class="card-link">See the evidence &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

